rgely unexplored, issues we must be most careful about as we move into an era of increasing numbers of parents exercising direct control over the genomes of their children.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 01. Dez 2022) 0aGenetic engineering. 0aGenetic screeningxMoral and ethical aspects. 0aGeneticsxMoral and ethical aspects. 7aMEDICAL / History.2bisacsh40uhttps://doi.org/10.12987/9780300262544?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780300262544423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780300262544/original  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aZDB-23-UCY